00b7a397f86ad26321a4bcb755bb4124b5eb0cf7.query:
SELECT SUM(views) page_views, date_trunc($4, recorded) as recorded_date
                FROM views
                WHERE views.project_id = $3 AND (views.recorded BETWEEN $1 AND $2)
                GROUP BY recorded_date
                ORDER BY 2 ASC;
